      • removeLast

        public P removeLast(Condition<P> c)
        Removes the last process from the queue that fulfills to the given condition, determined by traversing the queue from last to first until a process fulfilling the condition is found. Also provides a reference to this process. If the queue does not contain a process that fulfills the condition (e.g. if the queue is empty), null is returned.
        Overrides:
        removeLast in class ProcessQueue<P extends SimProcessAnimation>
        Parameters:
        c - Condition : The condition that the entity returned must fulfill
        Returns:
